<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Put your sword on your side, mighty one,</para>

<para style="q1">in your glory and your majesty.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />In your majesty ride on triumphantly</para>

<para style="q1">because of trustworthiness, meekness, and righteousness;</para>

<para style="q1">your right hand will teach you fearful things.</para>
